<button class="accordion">What are the four most common causes of violence and aggression?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The Encyclopaedia of Psychology defines violence as "an extreme form of aggression, such as assault, rape or murder." There are many causes of violence, including:</p>
<li>Frustration</li>
<li>Exposure to violent media</li>
<li>Violence in the home or neighbourhood</li>
<li>A tendency to see other people's actions as hostile even when they're not.</li><p></p>
